      <title>巴西财政部长应卢拉要求取消欧洲之行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/brazil-s-finance-chief-cancels-trip-to-europe-at-lula-s-request</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于雷亚尔持续下跌且政府考虑的削减开支幅度存在不确定性，巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 取消了本周的欧洲之行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/brazil-s-finance-chief-cancels-trip-to-europe-at-lula-s-request</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 14:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡办公室被指控泄密以阻碍加沙停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/war-in-gaza-netanyahu-s-office-accused-of-leaks-to-thwart-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两个月前，当以色列和哈马斯之间似乎即将达成停火协议时，一个新的障碍出现了：以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡表示，他的军队必须守住加沙和埃及边境，防止哈马斯重新武装并偷运出以色列人质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/war-in-gaza-netanyahu-s-office-accused-of-leaks-to-thwart-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 13:42:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
